OL,7,FYoni Finlay, who nearly lost his life
OL,8,Fin the Manchester synagogue attack in
OL,9,FOctober, tells ITV News North of
OL,10,FEngland Reporter Amy Welch how he has
OL,11,Fbeen struggling with survivor's guilt
OL,13,FA 39-year-old man who was shot with a
OL,14,Fpolice bullet has described seeing
OL,15,F"evil" in the eyes of the man who
OL,16,Fattacked his synagogue in Crumpsall,
OL,17,Fnorth Manchester.
