OL,7,FYoni Finlay was getting ready for Yom
OL,8,FKippur - the holiest day in the Jewish
OL,9,FCalendar - when Jihad Al-Shamie drove
OL,10,Fhis car into Heaton Park Hebrew
OL,11,FCongregation Synagogue on October 2.
OL,13,FA total of 37 people were inside.
OL,15,FMr Finlay described hearing a loud
OL,16,Fbang and barricading the doors
OL,17,Falongside other worshippers in an
OL,18,Fattempt to stop him from getting
OL,19,Finside. Al-Shamie had just run over a
OL,20,Fsecurity guard before stabbing two
OL,21,Fsecurity volunteers.
