OL,7,FArmed police arrived within minutes
OL,8,Fand opened fire. Al-Shamie was
OL,9,Fcarrying a large knife and had what
OL,10,Fappeared to be a bomb strapped around
OL,11,Fhis waist.
OL,13,FMr Finlay says he saw Al-Shamie run
OL,14,Ftowards police officers, who then
OL,15,Ffired more shots.
OL,17,FBut one of their bullets hit him
OL,18,Finstead.
OL,20,F"I knew straight away that I'd been
OL,21,Fshot," he told ITV News.
