OL,7,F"I remember thinking, I don't want to
OL,8,Fdie here.
OL,10,F"One step to the left or one step to
OL,11,Fthe right. Whichever way the bullet
OL,12,Fwas going, I wouldn't be here.
OL,14,F"But the same bullet that didn't kill
OL,15,Fme - Adrian wasn't so lucky."
OL,17,F"I remember thinking I don't want to
OL,18,Fdie here," Mr Finlay said
