OL,7,FThe police bullet penetrated the left
OL,8,Fside of his chest and exited through
OL,9,Fhis back, hitting 53-year-old Adrian
OL,10,FDaulby.
OL,12,FMr Daulby's been praised as a hero who
OL,13,Fdied trying to defend his place of
OL,14,Fworship.
OL,16,FMelvin Cravitz, 66, died of stab
OL,17,Fwounds, and two other men were injured.
