OL,7,FMr Finlay says he now struggles with
OL,8,Fsurvivor's guilt, but that he doesn't
OL,9,Fblame the police and the police
OL,10,Fwatchdog, the Independent Office for
OL,11,FPolice Conduct (IOPC), has found no
OL,12,Fevidence of police misconduct from
OL,13,Fthose firearms officers.
OL,15,F"The police, they run towards danger,"
OL,16,Fsaid Mr Finlay.
OL,18,F"They run towards the unknown.
