OL,7,F"They would put themselves in danger
OL,8,Fto protect us. The only person to
OL,9,Fblame here is the terrorist."
OL,11,FJihad Al-Shamie, a 35-year-old British
OL,12,Fcitizen of Syrian descent, dialled 999
OL,13,Fmoments after the attack to admit
OL,14,Fresponsibility and pledge his
OL,15,Fallegiance to the Islamic State.
OL,17,FCounter terrorism police say they
OL,18,Fweren't aware of him, and he was shot
OL,19,Fdead at the scene.
