OL,7,F"I think the atmosphere of hate and
OL,8,Fanger towards the Jews has been
OL,9,Fallowed to grow over the last two
OL,10,Fyears," said Mr Finlay.
OL,12,F"People are allowed to criticise,
OL,13,Fpeople are allowed to have opinions.
OL,14,FBut when those opinions spill over
OL,15,Finto hate and into anger, then that
OL,16,Fbecomes very difficult to to be able
OL,17,Fto live with."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
