OL,7,FMr Finlay says that although he was
OL,8,Fshocked at the attack, he wasn't
OL,9,Fsurprised, and that hatred towards
OL,10,FJews has been building since the
OL,11,FOctober 7 attacks in 2023
OL,13,FMr Finlay spent seven hours in surgery
OL,14,Fand was in the hospital for ten days.
OL,15,FPhysically, his wounds are healing,
OL,16,Fbut the psychological scars are still
OL,17,Fraw, and he says he fears for the
OL,18,Ffuture of his four children, whose
OL,19,Fschools and synagogues already have
OL,20,Fguards and gates.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
