OL,7,F"There's a lot of unknown uncertainty
OL,8,Fat the moment," said Mr Finlay.
OL,10,F"I'm just trying to live my life in a
OL,11,Fway that... I'm fortunate, I've been
OL,12,Fgiven another chance to, I was given
OL,13,Fmore time, and therefore, I can't
OL,14,Fwaste time."
OL,16,FThe Heaton Park Hebrew Congregation
OL,17,Fsynagogue has received 2,000 messages
OL,18,Fof support since the attack, and
OL,19,Fattendance is at an all-time high.
